  p Secure My Campus is a comprehensive platform designed to safeguard the well-being of students and ensure smooth functioning of campus life. It provides a safe and confidential space for reporting ragging or harassment complaints, reinforcing a zero-tolerance policy towards such incidents and promoting a respectful learning environment. The platform also supports a lost-and-found system to help students recover misplaced belongings easily. Additionally, it addresses food and canteen-related concerns by allowing feedback on hygiene, quality, and availability, ensuring healthy and student-friendly dining facilities. Hostel and campus maintenance issues, including problems with water, electricity, cleanliness, or infrastructure, can also be reported to guarantee a safe and comfortable living environment. By streamlining these processes, Secure My Campus acts as a bridge between students and administration, fostering a secure, supportive, and efficient campus experience.
